  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1531020/extras/7949da74f3a5d52b86f169c67c6476b5.poster.avif?t=1759779236\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1531020/extras/7949da74f3a5d52b86f169c67c6476b5.webm?t=1759779236\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1531020/extras/7949da74f3a5d52b86f169c67c6476b5.mp4?t=1759779236\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>SPECTRE is a thrilling competitive multiplayer experience featuring a combination of first and third person action gameplay.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1531020/extras/1e02d76eebb9e098af9de3d29b848db2.poster.avif?t=1759779236\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1531020/extras/1e02d76eebb9e098af9de3d29b848db2.webm?t=1759779236\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1531020/extras/1e02d76eebb9e098af9de3d29b848db2.mp4?t=1759779236\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The SPECTRES are an anonymous organization with members that consist of highly trained, acrobatic spies who excel at stealthily infiltrating well-protected compounds, obtaining top secret data and escaping undetected.​<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1531020/extras/d8477426d93d6252d7e99a34f73fe0c5.poster.avif?t=1759779236\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1531020/extras/d8477426d93d6252d7e99a34f73fe0c5.webm?t=1759779236\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1531020/extras/d8477426d93d6252d7e99a34f73fe0c5.mp4?t=1759779236\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>REAPERS, a well financed private military company, infamously only recruit the most skilled combatants from across the globe. They typically consist of former U.S. Marines who've abandoned 'Uncle Sam' in search of more bountiful compensation. The REAPERS are the heavily armed, lethal counter-measure for when the threat of a SPECTRE invasion looms.<br><br><br><br>Failure, for both sides, is not an option.<br><br>Players will experience the intense action gameplay from both perspectives, relying on their teammates to provide cover from - or distract- the opposing team as they race against the clock to complete their objectives.",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1531020/extras/7949da74f3a5d52b86f169c67c6476b5.poster.avif?t=1759779236\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1531020/extras/7949da74f3a5d52b86f169c67c6476b5.webm?t=1759779236\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1531020/extras/7949da74f3a5d52b86f169c67c6476b5.mp4?t=1759779236\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>SPECTRE is a thrilling competitive multiplayer experience featuring a combination of first and third person action gameplay.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1531020/extras/1e02d76eebb9e098af9de3d29b848db2.poster.avif?t=1759779236\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1531020/extras/1e02d76eebb9e098af9de3d29b848db2.webm?t=1759779236\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1531020/extras/1e02d76eebb9e098af9de3d29b848db2.mp4?t=1759779236\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The SPECTRES are an anonymous organization with members that consist of highly trained, acrobatic spies who excel at stealthily infiltrating well-protected compounds, obtaining top secret data and escaping undetected.​<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1531020/extras/d8477426d93d6252d7e99a34f73fe0c5.poster.avif?t=1759779236\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1531020/extras/d8477426d93d6252d7e99a34f73fe0c5.webm?t=1759779236\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1531020/extras/d8477426d93d6252d7e99a34f73fe0c5.mp4?t=1759779236\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>REAPERS, a well financed private military company, infamously only recruit the most skilled combatants from across the globe. They typically consist of former U.S. Marines who've abandoned 'Uncle Sam' in search of more bountiful compensation. The REAPERS are the heavily armed, lethal counter-measure for when the threat of a SPECTRE invasion looms.<br><br><br><br>Failure, for both sides, is not an option.<br><br>Players will experience the intense action gameplay from both perspectives, relying on their teammates to provide cover from - or distract- the opposing team as they race against the clock to complete their objectives.",
